{"version":1,"content":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20260419/s00024/188225cef33f4d4bb74da7bde188d6d8.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:1em\">荷蘭庫肯霍夫公園（Keukenhof）是世界著名的鬱金香花園，園內有數百種不同顏色鬱金香，此時正值鬱金香觀賞期，吸引大量遊客到訪，今年開放期至5月10日。（新華社）","scraped_at":"2026-04-21T01:42:08.456819+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":82,"images":1,"source":"明報 消閒","fallback":"rss-empty"}}